Definition: the first book of the Old Testament: tells of Creation
Example: Adam and Eve; the Fall of Man; Cain and Abel; Noah and the flood; God's covenant with Abraham; Abraham and Isaac; Jacob and Esau; Joseph and his brothers
Synonyms: Book_of_Genesis, book, i, Torah, p, Old_Testament, the, first, of, Old, Testament, tells, Creation, Adam, and, Eve, Fall, Man, Cain, Abel, Noah, flood, God, s, covenant, with, Abraham, Isaac, Jacob, Esau, Joseph, his, brothers
Category: noun.communication
